  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿！有传言说有人拿到了Ryba的日记。我们现在可以行动了！我想是本地经销商之一，我就知道！这些贪婪的混蛋，从一开始就很清楚。\n\n你知道我需要这本日记，而且我知道你需要钱、装备以及你们行动人员日常杀戮和掠夺所需的其他任何东西。如果你把日记带给我，你所得到的回报远比日记对你而言更有价值，我保证，只要把它带给我，你不会后悔，但你会后悔把它给了别人。所以仔细考虑你的立场。",
    "en": "Hey there! Word got around that someone obtained Ryba's diary. We can make our move now! I think it's one of the local dealers, I knew it! These greedy assholes, it was clear from the very beginning.\n\nYou know that I need this diary, and I know that you need money, gear and whatever else you operators require for your daily killing and looting. What you receive if you bring me the diary is way more valuable than the diary will ever be to you, I promise, just bring it to me, you won't regret it but you will regret it giving it to someone else. So consider your position carefully."
  },
